## Running Tests

1. After setting up the virtual environment and installing dependencies, you can run the tests with:

   ```bash
   PYTHONPATH=src pytest tests/
   ```

2. Alternatively, you can modify the `pytest.ini` or your test files as explained in the setup instructions above to ensure imports work correctly.

## Contributing

Feel free to fork the repository, submit issues, or contribute directly. Please ensure that you write unit tests for any new features or bug fixes.


